	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><strong>Yes.</strong>
<br />
<br />VRAM is video random access memory, meaning any RAM primarily used by a video chip. CHR RAM is a type of VRAM, usually 8 KiB in size unless bankswitched.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


